 not curse time, Allah is Time","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty said: The son of Adam insults Me. He curses time, but I am time, for in My hand are the night and day.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 4826, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2246 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1814,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/01\/09\/decreed-portion-of-zina\/","url_meta":{"origin":2562,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Zina: Allah decreed for everyone a portion of adultery","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has decreed upon the son of Adam his portion of adultery that he will inevitably commit: the adultery of the two eyes is a lustful look, the adultery of the tongue is obscene speech. The soul\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40536,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/03\/women-hajj-menstruation\/","url_meta":{"origin":2562,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Menses: Women performing Hajj will menstruating","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2023","format":false,"exc